					<div class="col-md-6 px-0 px-md-4 pe-md-0"> 
						<div class="card-body form-card">
							<h2 class="card-title mb-4">Stay up to date with The Scoop</h2>
							<div class="card-text"><p>Sign up to receive Battersea emails and receive The Scoop straight to your inbox, our newsletter with all the latest news from behind-the-scenes at Battersea, including animal updates and more.</p>
<p>By completing this form, you are confirming that you are 18 or over.</p>
</div>
