				<div class="row privacy-content">
					<div class="col-md-12">
						<h5>Your privacy rights&nbsp;</h5>
<p>By subscribing to Battersea emails, you’ll receive news, updates about our animals, information about rehoming and how you can support Battersea with fundraising, volunteering, events and campaigning. Battersea will treat your information with respect and use it only to send you the emails you have requested unless you have previously supported Battersea.&nbsp;</p>
<p>If you would like us not to contact you by post, or want to change the way we communicate with you at any time, please contact our <a href="https://www.battersea.org.uk/about-us/contact-us">Supporter Services team</a>. Further information about how we protect and use your personal data is available in our <a href="https://www.battersea.org.uk/privacy-policy-and-cookies-policy">Privacy Policy</a>.</p>

					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
				</div>
      </div>

</div>
